line-height: 1.5;\"><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; line-height: 1.5; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">c:\\</pre></pre><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\">After that</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\"><pre style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">c:\\&gt; cd xampp</pre><pre style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">c:\\xampp&gt;cd htdocs<br>c:\\xampp\\www&gt; cls</pre></pre><p data-adtags-visited=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"\" noto=\"\" serif\",=\"\" serif;\"=\"\">Check composer install or not</span></p><pre style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; line-height: 1.5; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">c:\\xampp\\htdocs&gt;composer</pre></pre><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\">After installing the new project<br></pre><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"Capture.JPG\" style=\"width: 50%;\"><br></p><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"\" noto=\"\" serif\",=\"\" serif;\"=\"\"><pre style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; line-height: 1.5; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span noto=\"\" serif\",=\"\" serif;\"=\"\">c:\\xampp\\htdocs&gt;composer create-project laravel/laravel MyFirstProjectName</span></pre></pre></span></pre><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\">Don’t close CMD wait for the download and installed laravel its depends on your internet speed.</p><p data-adtags-visited=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5;\">Enjoy :)<br></p>', '5bf56ad36c011af2.jpeg', 'how-to-install-composer-on-windows.html', 'Y', 'How to Install Composer on Windows', NULL, '2020-08-11 18:36:52', '2020-08-12 09:05:14');

