(2, 'harhukams@gmail.com', '<div class=\"faqs\" style=\"\"><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: I get an error using the confirmation email.<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: Please follow the steps below to resolve this issue:</span></p><ul style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px 35px; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin: 5px 0px;\">First, try logging in (with the email address you signed up with).</li><li style=\"margin: 5px 0px;\">If you are unable to log in, please copy and paste the full URL (web address) of the link that you received in the confirmation email into your browser.</li><li style=\"margin: 5px 0px;\">If you\'re still having trouble after the above steps, send us an email on <a href=\"mailto:feedback@speakingtree.in\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\">feedback@speakingtree.in</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: My confirmation email didn\'t arrive.<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: Please follow the steps below to resolve this issue:</span></p><ul style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px 35px; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin: 5px 0px;\">Check your email application\'s spam or junk folder or filter. Please be aware that some emails may be blocked by your ISP (Internet Service Provider).</li><li style=\"margin: 5px 0px;\">Check that you\'re trying to log in from the exact email address you registered with. A common error is registering with an incorrect email domain (e.g., @indiatimes.com is not the same as @indiatimes.co.in). In addition, keep in mind that email addresses never begin with a \"www\" prefix.</li><li style=\"margin: 5px 0px;\">If you\'re still having trouble after the above steps, send us an email on <a href=\"mailto:feedback@speakingtree.in\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\">feedback@speakingtree.in</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: I received an account creation email, but I\'m already registered.<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: If you have received an account confirmation email in error, it\'s likely that someone has mistakenly attempted to register using your email address. As long as you do not click the link contained in the email, no action will be taken, and no account will be created. Please disregard these emails.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: While signing up it says the account already exists.<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: If you are the account owner and are attempting to sign up for another account, then please be aware that you can only sign up for one account per email address. If you are an existing itimes or Indiatimes user, please sign in using those credentials.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: I am a registered itimes / Indiatimes user, do I still need to sign up.<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: You can login with your existing itimes/ Indiatimes credentials. You don\'t need to create a separate Speaking tree account for login.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: It says my email address is invalid.p<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: Please recheck the email id you are entering. It should be of format xyz@abc.com where \"xyx\" is the username and \"abc\" is the domain name. Also please be aware that that you can only sign up for one account per email address.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: The \"words in the box\" (i.e., captchas) doesn\'t load.<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: Your problem is most likely related to your internet browser. We recommend that you upgrade your browser, or clear its cache and cookies for smooth workflow.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: What do I need to do to sign up for this site?<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: From our Sign Up page, just provide us with your full name, email address, desired password, and gender. You also get an option to select a master, provide date of birth and choosing a faith. Once you furnish the info we require, you will receive an activation email on the email id you provided while registering. Please follow the steps given in the email properly to complete the registration process.<br><br>After you complete the sign up form, we will send an email to the address you provided. Clicking on the Activation link will complete the sign up process.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"Bottom_brdr\" style=\"\"><h1 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 1.1; padding-bottom: 5px;\">Login and Password</h1></div><div class=\"faqs\" style=\"\"><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: How do I change my password?<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: If you know your password and would like to change it, you can do so from the Accounts tab on settings page. If you don\'t remember your password, you can reset it by clicking forgot password link on the signin popup.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"Bottom_brdr\" style=\"\"><h1 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 1.1; padding-bottom: 5px;\">Profile</h1></div><div class=\"faqs\" style=\"\"><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: How do I edit my profile privacy settings?<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: You can adjust your profile privacy settings from the account tab in the Profile setting page. Privacy Settings option are at the bottom of the page. You can select Pubic option to make it searchable.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: How can I control who can see my profile information and post to my Wall?<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: If your profile is Public then everyone will be able to see your profile information, However if your profile is Private, Only you can see your profile.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: How do I edit my profile?<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: You can adjust your profile by clicking edit profile link on your profile page.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\">Q: What are the different profile badges on Speaking Tree?<span style=\"display: block; margin: 5px 0px 0px 20px;\">A: Profile badges are different levels you attain in your spiritual journey on Speaking Tree. To know more <a href=\"http://www.speakingtree.in/my_badge.php?uid=1\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\">click here</a>.</span></p></div><div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"><p sty